# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  NOVA AI Bot — Environment Variables
#  Render.com pe ye sab "Environment Variables" mein dalo
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── REQUIRED ──────────────────────────────────────
BOT_TOKEN=1234567890:ABCdefGHIjklMNOpqrSTUvwxYZ
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSyXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
MONGO_URI=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/
ADMIN_IDS=987654321

# ── RENDER WEBHOOK ────────────────────────────────
# Deploy hone ke baad apna Render URL yahan dalo
RENDER_URL=https://nova-ai-bot.onrender.com

# ── OPTIONAL (defaults already set) ──────────────
ADMIN_USERNAME=your_telegram_username
MONGO_DB_NAME=nova_ai_bot
FREE_DAILY_LIMIT=30
PREMIUM_DAILY_LIMIT=9999
PORT=8443
